Resource Profile: CH EMED EPR Practitioner

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-emed-epr/StructureDefinition/ch-emed-epr-practitioner Version: 3.0.0
Draft as of 2026-02-11 Computable Name: CHEMEDEPRPractitioner

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

Definition of the practitioner for the eMedication context

Usages:

  • Use this Profile: PMLC Document, DIS Document, PML Document, PRE Document... Show 2 more, MTP Document and PADV Document
  • Refer to this Profile: PMLC Composition, DIS Composition, PML Composition, PRE Composition... Show 3 more, MTP Composition, PADV Composition and CH EMED EPR PractitionerRole
  • Examples for this Profile: Practitioner/PharmacistDoe and Practitioner/PractitionerCox

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
